Titolo: Shin Megami Tensei V

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Shin Megami Tensei V is a 2021 post-apocalyptic role-playing video game developed by Atlus and published by Sega for the Nintendo Switch. Released in November, it is part of the Shin Megami Tensei series, the central series of the larger Megami Tensei franchise. Produced by Shin Megami Tensei IV director Kazuyuki Yamai, it was designed as a hybrid between Shin Megami Tensei III: Nocturne and Shin Megami Tensei IV, featuring returning gameplay mechanics such as raising and fusing demons.